---
title: Caesar Crunch Chicken with Parmesan Frico Roasted Veggies
description: Caesar is not just for salads anymore! In fact, that creamy, tantalizingly tangy dressing has finally found its rightful home—adorning crunchy coated chicken cutlets. Plus, we’ve ditched the lettuce and croutons for a surprising side that may just rock your world: crispy frico veggies. (Translation: tender roasted carrots and green beans topped with crispy baked Parmesan cheese.) After one bite, we know you’ll hail it a success.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6142108d5a5f4243a879978a-b386ee71.jpg
